 spectroscopy, and summarize existing reports on ferroelectric like\nresponses in non-classical ferroelectric materials. We further discuss possible\nmechanisms behind observed behaviors, and possible experimental strategies for\ntheir identification.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 4 Jan 2017 19:18:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-01-06"}
